---
import InfoLayout from '../layouts/InfoLayout.astro';
---

<InfoLayout
  title="Pricing · StudentLancers"
  description="StudentLancers charges a flat 8% fee on completed work. No subscription, no setup fee, no card to join."
  eyebrow="Pricing"
  heading="Simple, flat, and aligned with the work."
  lead="StudentLancers charges an 8% platform fee on completed engagements. No subscription, no setup fee, no minimum. Students keep the rest."
>
  <h2>What companies pay</h2>
  <p>
    Companies post briefs for free. When a brief is funded, the platform fee
    is deducted on completion and the student is paid the rest. Students and
    companies are free to choose their preferred payment method and payment
    terms.
  </p>

  <h2>What students pay</h2>
  <p>
    Nothing to join. The 8% fee is deducted only on work that's been paid for.
    No proposals, no boosts, no monthly subscriptions.
  </p>

  <h2>Examples</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>$1,200 fixed brief.</strong> Company pays $1,200, student is paid $1,104 on approval.</li>
    <li><strong>$45/hr × 12 hours.</strong> Company funds $540, student is paid $496.80.</li>
    <li><strong>Cancelled engagement.</strong> Full refund minus any non-recoverable payment-processor fees.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Payment processing</h2>
  <p>
    Funds move through Stripe Connect. StudentLancers never holds your money
    in our own bank account — payouts route directly to the student via the
    method they choose.
  </p>

  <h2>Need a custom plan?</h2>
  <p>
    If you're hiring more than 20 students a quarter, we can set up an
    enterprise agreement with invoicing, custom contracts, and a dedicated
    success contact. <a href="/contact">Talk to sales</a>.
  </p>
</InfoLayout>
